WEBVTT

00:06:29.042 --> 00:06:30.333
should I build it?

00:06:31.750 --> 00:06:35.393
By open-sourcing the lab
to encourage access and inclusivity,

00:06:35.417 --> 00:06:38.851
I also run the risk
of enabling powerful governments

00:06:38.875 --> 00:06:41.809
and profit-driven companies
to appropriate the platform

00:06:41.833 --> 00:06:45.917
for fake news, marketing
or other forms of mass persuasion.

00:06:47.375 --> 00:06:50.726
For me, therefore,
it is critical to make my research

00:06:50.750 --> 00:06:54.333
as transparent to
lay audiences as GMO labels.

00:06:55.333 --> 00:06:57.875
However, this is not enough.

00:06:59.208 --> 00:07:00.851
As creative technologists,